{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The game does not support English at this time. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>If you need, please join the wish list, we will join the development plan as appropriate,</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong> thank you!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Stage of Tale</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story takes place in the imprisoned city <i>Leliana</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enveloped by an eerie white fog, no one can find an escape, not even in death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This also involves 'you,' who are not of humankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/1-CITY2.png?t=1739930289\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A young bearing a mission, a scholar delving into the death, a &quot;blood relative&quot; consumed by madness, and a saintess in a death-like trance\u2026\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will encounter a diverse array of characters, all interwoven in the tapestry of fate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u89d2\u8272-L.png?t=1739930289\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u89d2\u8272-\u62c9\u6cd5\u53f6.png?t=1739930289\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u89d2\u8272-\u5965\u4e3d\u5f17.png?t=1739930289\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u89d2\u8272-\u963f\u5c14\u514b\u83b1.png?t=1739930289\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Branching Story Paths</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this journey, the secrets of the kingdom and the truths of the world are gradually revealed. Confronted by a world on the brink, you wield the power to redeem or to unravel. Each fork in the road unfurls a distinct chapter of fate, with the very survival of characters hinging on your decisions.The outcome of this adventure will be revealed in your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u9009\u62e9.gif?t=1739930289\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a card combat system enriched with RPG elements, where exploiting weaknesses and coordinating with teammates are key to overcoming adversaries with strategic prowess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u6218\u6597.gif?t=1739930289\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Vibrant Exploration</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the top-down map, investigating designated scenes for a detailed inquiry. Engage in disputes with black market blacksmiths or uncover notes hinting at hidden treasures, with every encounter feeling organically intertwined in the fabric of this vivid world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/extras/\u63a2\u7d22.gif?t=1739930289\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">contact <a href=\"mailto:us\uff1amxuan12@qq.com\">us\uff1amxuan12@qq.com</a></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2996660?t=1739930289","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739930289","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739930289","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2996660/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=17399302